{"tid":508741,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"我無得過聖誕節真係無癮","createTime":"2017-12-24T14:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T07:10:03.000Z","uid":9683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"efd2127d6744b915f0f121924258c97bc70e02af","tid":508741,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:12:22.000Z","msg":"我無得過聖誕節真係無癮<br />\n我啲friends通通去玩掉低我<br />\n我無得唱聖誕歌同埋佈置聖誕樹<br />\n究竟係個天玩我定係我嘅&hellip;錯?<br />\n我屋企唔相信耶穌曾經係出過世<br />\n我好慘 我好很慘 無聖誕節&hellip;<br />\n我冇得過聖誕節真係冇癮<br />\n聖誕老人年年都唔理我<br />\n每次得我一個人兼夾羨慕人開心<br />\n究竟係我投錯胎定係改壞名?<br />\n我好想有個人可以解釋俾我聽<br />\n我好慘 我好很慘 <br />\n我會結婚 但唔生仔<br />\n無聖&hellip;誕節&hellip;<br />\n#我好慘 #我好很慘 #無聖誕節<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nikuniku/videos/1578551275565122/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnikuniku%2Fvideos%2F1578551275565122%2F&d=AwnFYw5fpi2uRqQmtchf6v9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f165427b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nikuniku/videos/1578551275565122/</a>"},{"pid":"a8a620418a683ce6bf234b4f67a2767120be3215","tid":508741,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44260cc68d14314902fd3e2fca1b9743061db725","tid":508741,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ab1a754c2b81362b3d83ee7c05d3983328d326","tid":508741,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4fdac446a18e03d70830a431b57215222f1624","tid":508741,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr